    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is currently in running order, though it will require some attention to bring it back to its best. The engine starts and the car is drivable, but you may notice some minor mechanical quirks and a bit of hesitation during acceleration. Cosmetically, there are visible scratches and some fading in the paint, along with minor interior wear such as a few stains on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid candidate for someone looking for a dependable base vehicle who doesn't mind doing some light maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
      "price": 18500.0,
