    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit exhibits superior mechanical integrity and a documented service history, ensuring consistent performance and long-term reliability. The interior and exterior maintain a sophisticated presentation, reflecting a standard of care that distinguishes this offering within the current market. An ideal acquisition for those seeking an optimal balance of value and prestige.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been a total joy to drive\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, making it the perfect pick if you want a dependable ride that feels just right. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. The subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary weak point. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, and the throttle response remains razor-sharp thanks to the individual throttle bodies. A true enthusiast's specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, showing only the minor, honest signs of road use that one would expect from a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the upholstery is clean and supportive, and all onboard technology\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, a testament to a consistent service schedule and proactive care. While it carries the character of a seasoned traveler, its mechanical integrity and overall presentation make it a reliable and stylish choice for daily commutes or weekend getaways. This is a complete package for someone seeking quality and performance without the premium of a showroom-floor price.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and in commendable mechanical standing, this automobile offers a refined driving experience complemented by a well-preserved interior and exterior. It serves as a testament to enduring engineering and remains a premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking proven reliability. An exceptional acquisition for those who demand quality without compromise.",
      "price": 36450.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s had some fun adventures and definitely has plenty more left in the tank. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next chapter, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the critical VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high torque loads. The factory M-Variable limited-slip differential provides superb mechanical grip, while the chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and dampers. While showing honest patina consistent with its enthusiast history, the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory spec and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A mechanically sound, high-revving machine optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
